- **连续零新发现轮次：** {{ '{{ zero_new_finding_streak }}' }}/{{ convergence_rounds }}
- **累计轮次：** {{ '{{ current_round }}' }}/{{ max_cycles }}
- **状态：** [IN_PROGRESS | WAITING_FOR_REVIEW | CONVERGED | HARD_STOP | ESCAPE_DETECTED]
```

